description	"Wild Wampa 

A feral animal looking for its next meal. Not a particularly picky eater.

^2Weaponry:
- Wild Beast (Limited Melee)
-- 600% more Dmg
-- Barge only
- Claws (Stun Baton 1)
-- 200% more Dmg
-- 15% faster Movement
-- 140% slower RoF

^5Powers:
- Dark Rage (3) ^3[CS1]

^8Attributes:
- 40% faster Skill Cd
- 80% less Kb Taken
- 400% slower Hacking
- No Gunbash
- No weapon pickups
- Strength (3)
- Fury (3)
-- 35% slower Resource Decay
- Healing (2)
-- Extra HP Regen: 5/20s
- Base Dmg Taken 
- Blast Armor
- Physical Resist

^3Abilities:
- Lunge (Barge) ^3[CS2 Melee]"